quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,By the fig! And by the olive
  95,2,And by Mount Sinai
  95,3,And by this safe land
  95,4,We have indeed created man in the best of symmetry
  95,5,Then we will send him back the lowest of the low
  95,6,save those who believe and act aright; for theirs is a hire that is not grudged
  95,7,But what shall make thee call the judgment after this a lie
  95,8,Is not God a most just of judges